    "description": "《Vernal Edge》是一款动感十足的 2D 类银河恶魔城游戏，具有激烈的战斗系统和紧凑的平台序列，讲述了一个关于对抗、复仇和成长的有力故事。<br> <br>魔豆王国完全是个谜。在故事发生的 20 年前，它凭空出现，升上天空，变成了许多相互分离的浮岛。这让渴望权力的芦荟教会占领了这片大陆。<br> <br>熙春对教会及其代理人不屑一顾，她偷偷溜进教会的一架飞行器，从而来到了魔豆王国。她是一位独立的冒险家，在穿越魔豆王国的同时，也试图向消失已久的混蛋父亲复仇。凭借着自身超凡的武艺，再加上失忆机器人香芹的帮助，她驾驶着自己的飞行器穿过王国的不同岛屿。<br> <br>你将扮演熙春，通过她的眼睛去探索她的目标；在浮岛上遭遇各种敌人，比如神出鬼没的六出花。在杀出一条血路的同时，揭露关于她的过去和魔豆王国的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2> <br><strong>快节奏的银河战士恶魔城游戏</strong><br>探索芸都的浮岛。不要放过城镇和地宫的任何一个角落，新的力量可能就在意想不到之处！跳跃、冲刺、滑行，尽情享受充满艺术气息的的像素场景。记住：秘密或许就在你的身旁！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a203dc37ec862e13f3280f9f07ca0b0c.poster.avif?t=1748596507\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a203dc37ec862e13f3280f9f07ca0b0c.webm?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a203dc37ec862e13f3280f9f07ca0b0c.mp4?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>成就感爆棚的动态战斗系统</strong><br>精进春熙的连击与术法，施展出最致命的组合技摧毁敌人！没有一场战斗拘泥于固定战术，《Vernal Edge》时时刻刻都能给玩家带来新的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/af3027e768fb7c6be83fa7946f34d53b.poster.avif?t=1748596507\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/af3027e768fb7c6be83fa7946f34d53b.webm?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/af3027e768fb7c6be83fa7946f34d53b.mp4?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>在游戏中开辟自己的道路</strong><br>燃起心中的火焰，乘风自由翱翔！飞行器带你在《Vernal Edge》的浮岛间任意穿梭，探索的道路完全掌握在你自己手中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a309bd900b7b95e1764d0e1da44b2b4f.poster.avif?t=1748596507\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a309bd900b7b95e1764d0e1da44b2b4f.webm?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1546710/extras/a309bd900b7b95e1764d0e1da44b2b4f.mp4?t=1748596507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>揭开芸都的神秘面纱，与春熙并肩快意恩仇。",
